window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Life is full of choices. Right now, yours is whether or not to buy the autobiography of a mid-grade, kind of hammy actor. </p> <p><i>Am I supposed to know this guy?</i> you think to yourself.</p> <p>No, and that's exactly the point. The truth is that though you might not have a clue who I am, there are countless working stiffs like me out there, grinding away every day at the wheel of fortune. </p> <p><i>If Chins Could Kill: Confessions of a B Movie Actor</i> is my first book, and I invite you to ride with me through the choppy waters of blue collar Hollywood. </p> <p>Okay, so buy the damned book already! </p>"; 
